item.title: Absolutely Fabulous
item.description: I saw a post the other day that made me laugh… “None of this new year new me bollocks, last year I was fabulous and next year I will be fabulous!” Very amusing, and vaguely relevant to me, I’m fabulous some days, possibly two days a week, but honestly, I think it’s BS. Maybe not a new me, but a better version of myself wouldn’t hurt, perhaps like a software update!
